descript.abstract: Polygon shapefile of approximately 2-km radar rainfall pixels created by OneRain Inc. This layer can be related to tables that contain daily rainfall data.
descript.purpose: The shapefile is used to display gage-adjusted radar rainfall estimates from OneRain Inc.
descript.supplinf: Pixel numbering is for the entire state of Florida.

attracc.attraccr: The SWFWMD pixel numbering were compared to teh numbering for the shapefile of radar pixels for the entire state of Florida.

dataqual.complete: Shapefile is complete and includes all pixels within 30 miles of the SWFWMD bounday over land and 2 miles over ocean.

horizpa.horizpar: The shapefile of radar pixels over Florida was verified against the positional attributes of OneRain's radar pixel shapefile for the entire country. Accuracy is within +/- 0.000001 degrees.
